Wealth Management














It takes a strategy to make the most of what wealth can bring to your life. Not just any strategy, however—your strategy.
Supported by more than 35 professionals, including trust administrators, tax accountants, estate settlement specialists, and philanthropy advisors, the Private Client Group lawyers of the international law firm, Ropes & Gray LLP, can provide you with holistic advice. 
The Private Client Group has represented individuals and families for more than a century and is one of the largest practices of its kind in the United States. 
Together, our sole mission is to help you manage your wealth so it has a positive impact on your life and the lives of generations to come. 







An International Reach



Cross border wealth transfer issues require experienced legal advice and skilled coordination with foreign counsel. Both U.S. and foreign families and entrepreneurs can depend on Ropes & Gray and its experience in representing individuals and fiduciaries worldwide. An interdisciplinary approach is vitally important for all international planning situations. 










































