At Ropes Wealth Advisors, we are committed to providing financial insights and education to our clients in the areas of investment management, financial planning, and a broad range of wealth management topics. We dive deeply into questions of importance and are passionate about providing truly valuable solutions. 
We author regular investment commentaries and white papers to stimulate discussion and participation in exploring important ideas. We also welcome clients and friends of the firm to attend educational workshops and conferences to discuss key wealth management topics in a dynamic forum. 







Leading by Example Conference



The Boston Foundation, Boston College and Ropes & Gray LLP presented their inaugural conference on charitable giving, Leading by Example, at The Conference Center at University of Massachusetts Boston, Campus Center on October 20, 2016. The conference provided a forum for professional advisors, family office leaders, planned giving and development professionals, and donors to share their experiences, review recent developments, discuss best practices, learn from other experts, and express their passion for philanthropy. 
Opening remarks by Paul Grogan, President and CEO of The Boston Foundation.
