Our Investment Approach














Our team is proud of our tradition of investment experience, integrity, and devotion to you. Our approach incorporates:
Customization: Ropes Wealth does not believe in off-the-shelf standardized solutions; we build investment plans only after we have listened to you and have understood your objectives and risk tolerance.
Transparency: Ropes Wealth does not sell investment products, and we do not profit from your choice of investment vehicles.
Institutional quality: Ropes Wealth's team of seasoned investment professionals are dedicated to your particular needs, and seek to bring you the best solutions, technology, and tools available in the marketplace.
Risk management: We strive to control risk through sophisticated asset allocation and access to high quality investment managers and vehicles.

Tax sensitivity: We recognize that it is not just the money you earn, it is the money you keep, so we make tax sensitivity an ongoing process, from portfolio structure to continuous monitoring to manager selection.







You are our Focus



Investing is not a competitive sport. The most important role we play as your investment advisor is to design an investment strategy which is crafted to reflect your objectives, preferences and temperament so as to give you the greatest likelihood of achieving your lifetime financial goals. We are not artificially driven by an attempt to beat the performance of an index that happens to be “hot” at the moment, nor do we attempt to time the movements of the financial markets.










































Ropes Wealth Advisors: Income Tax Advising



























Client Login











































Income Tax Advising
Ropes & Gray believes good income tax planning is integral to sound wealth management.







Income Tax Advising














Today’s tax laws are less certain and more complex than ever. Keeping abreast of the latest developments and tax-minimization strategies can be overwhelming.  Ropes & Gray will set out your options and choices so you can make informed decisions.  
Ropes & Gray’s Private Client Group lawyers and income tax professionals provide expertise in all areas of income tax advising, and will partner with you to develop solutions to your questions. Ropes & Gray’s broad experience extends over such areas as retirement planning and charitable giving, as well as techniques to make income tax efficient gifts and loans to family members. Ropes & Gray can help you achieve your objectives and minimize your income tax burden, thereby preserving your wealth.  







Make Plans for Your Plan



Have you considered the heavy income tax burden associated with your retirement plan? It may be wise to pay some tax now and convert your traditional IRA to a Roth IRA. Alternatively, if you are over 70½, you may be able to make contributions to charity directly from your retirement plan, in lieu of taking required minimum distributions. Ropes & Gray can help you consider the availability and advisability of these and other approaches to reducing your income taxes.









































